<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink66-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">putalvaṉaip piriyātavaṉ pirintu puṟattut taṅki vantāṉāka, avaṉōṭu pulantu talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink66">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>uṭaliṉē ṉallēṉ poyyā turaimō</l>
<l>yāravaṇ makiḻna tāṉē tēroṭu</l>
<l>taḷarnaṭaip putalvaṉai yuḷḷiniṉ</l>
<l>vaḷamaṉai varutalum vauvi yōḷē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">



<l>   I am not angry, [so] tell me without lying: </l> 
 <p/>
<l> She who, </l> 
 <l> remembering [our] son with his faltering steps and chariot, </l> 
<l> snatches [him] as soon as she comes to your prosperous home –  </l> 
<p/>
<l> (OR: She who foiled [your] return to your proserous home</l> 
<l> [even] when you'd remembered [our] son, with his faltering steps, and [your] chariot –)   </l> 
<p/>
<l> Who is that woman? [Tell me], o delightful man! </l> 



</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
